msgstr "i2c_bus - 要使用的I2C总线号。"

#: ../../library/omv.rpc.rst:307 ../../library/omv.rpc.rst:325
msgid ""
"NOTE: Master and slave addresses must match. Connect master scl to slave "
"scl and master sda to slave sda. You must use external pull ups. Finally,"
" both devices must share a ground."
msgstr "注意：主和从地址必须匹配。将主scl连接到从scl，将主sda连接到从sda。您必须使用外部上拉电阻。最后，两个设备必须共享地线。"

